quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,49,"Haddaysan Nicmad xagga Rabbigi ah haleesheen, waxaa lagu tuuri lahaa cidla’ bannaan isagoo eedeysan."
  68,50,"Rabbigiis baase doortay, kana mid yeelay kuwa wanaagsan."
  68,51,"Kuwaa gaalada ahise waxay sigaan inay kugu gubaan indhahooda (dhabatoda) naceyb gala awgiis markay maqlaan Waanada (Qur’aankan); waxayna yidhaahdaan: Kani waa jinnoole."
  69,46,"Oo waxaan goyn laheyn halbowlaha."
  69,47,"Ma jiro qof idinka mid ahi oo naga celin lahaa."
  69,48,"(Qur'aanku) waa u waano kuwa ka dhowrsada xumaha ee Alle u hoggaansan."
  70,40,"Mayee se! Waxaan ku dhaartay Rabbiga bariyada iyo galbeedyada (waa isla Alle'e oo naf ahaantiisa ku dhaaran) inaan Karno;"
  70,41,"Inaan ku beddelno (kuwo kale) oo ka wanaagsan; nalagamana adkaado."
  70,42,"Ee iska dhaaf ha dhumbadeene (xumaanta) hana iska cayaareen, intay kala kulmaan Maalinkooda loogu gooddiyo."
  74,25,"Kanu (Qur'aanku) ma aha waxaan aheyn hadal Aadmi."
  74,26,"Waxaan galin kaasi Saqaro (Naar)."
  74,27,"Maxaad ka og tahay waxay Saqaro tahay?"
  75,22,"Wejiyo Maalintaas way ifi."
  75,23,"Xagga (Alle) Rabbigood iyagoo eegaya;"
  75,24,"Wejiyo (kale) Maalintaas waxay ahaan kuwo kuduudsan."
  76,16,"Quraarado fiddo (qalin) ah si fiicanna u qiyaasan."
  76,17,"Waxaa laga waraabin galaas (khamro saafi ah) lagu dheehay Sanjabiil,"
  76,18,"Il (Jannada)gudaheeda ah, la yidhaahdo Salsabiil."
  77,13,"Maalinta kala baxa (Qiyaamada)."
  77,14,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyey waxay Maalinta kala baxu tahay?"
  77,15,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  78,10,"Oo ka dhigin habeenka hu’ oo kale (idinku daboola mugdigiisa)?,"
  78,11,"Oo ka dhigin maalinta maciishad raadin,"
  78,12,"Oo ka dhisin korkiinna toddobo (samo) oo adadag?."
  79,4,"Iyo (malaa'igta) u dheereeya 'khayrka iyo wanaagga' dheereyn."
  79,5,"Iyo (malaa'igta) isku duwa arrin (walba) (si waafaqsan amarka Alle, in dadow la idin soo bixin oo xisaabin Aakhirada)."
  79,6,"Maalinta ay gilgilatadu gilgilan (waa afuufka hore ee Buunka)."
  80,1,"(Wejiguu) kuduuday oo jeesaday (Nebiga s.c.w),"
  80,2,"Inuu u yimid indhoolihii{2} darteed,",footnotes:1:. Waa Cabdullaah ibn Um Maktuum a.k.r.,footnotes:2:
  80,3,"Miyaad ogtahay (Nabiyow) waa intaasoo uu hanuuno oo daahir noqdo,"